     As Rodimus crushes the boulder Vampirtron leaps out of the woods. A surge of energon takes him and he falls to his knees. &quot;AHHHH!!!!!!&quot; He yells, &quot;Beast mode!&quot; He transforms to the large black wolf that he is, but the energon still is running through him, &quot;Ahhh, it burns!&quot; Finally, after about a minute of agony, it stops.
     &quot;I can&#39;t take pure energon,&quot; Vampirtron said to himself, &quot;I can&#39;t hold it at all. That must be why I have to feed on other transformers. Rodimus, I don&#39;t know how long I can last without feeding on other Transformers. I may become a danger to yourself and your Maximals. I will try to hold it, but if I can&#39;t, you must lock me away.&quot;
